            </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" onclick="let rid=$('#reportee2id').val();let mid=$('#messageid').val();AjaxRequestJson(`${rid}/messages/${mid}`, GetForms, {'<>':'li','html': '${href} ${name}'},'#forms')">Get forms</a></p>
